data.description: Sellers are offering a $5000 mortgage rate buy-down on acceptable offers! Opportunity awaits in this beautifully constructed four bedroom, two bath house in one of Rockport’s newest neighborhoods, Wandering Oaks! You’re greeted with simple and elegant landscaping, detailed with dark gray river rock. Step into the formal foyer, open to the kitchen, dining and living area. This highly desired open floor plan is appointed with tile floors, neutral color palette, oversized granite island with seating for six. The white cottage style cabinets, large pantry & smooth top stove make spending time in this kitchen a delight. Retreat to the spacious main bedroom featuring a raised tray ceiling with crown molding, and luxury en suite. Relax after a long day on the water in the soaking tub or enjoy the tiled shower with rainshower head. The additional three bedrooms will comfortably sleep your guests or family. Love the outdoors? The solar screen porch makes a perfect place to kick back. The storage building conveys. What are you waiting for? Make an appointment today!
